00:27:33.069 --> 00:27:36.280
Over there,
that's the tag and bag. Sir? Sir?

329
00:27:36.447 --> 00:27:39.075
Through those doors, that's 10-17.
Roger.

330
00:27:39.242 --> 00:27:40.326
Carlson?
Yes, sir.

331
00:27:40.493 --> 00:27:41.828
Show him the rest later.
- Oh, yeah.

332
00:27:42.036 --> 00:27:43.579
Come on.
