it was pretty cool. I got pretty good at it.

350
00:28:45.641 --> 00:28:50.313
You know, you don't have to stop for the yellow.
You could just drive right through. It's all right.

351
00:28:50.521 --> 00:28:54.567
Sir, not if you'd seen some of the accidents I've seen.
No, thanks.

352
00:28:56.402 --> 00:28:58.571
Well, there's your green right there.

353
00:29:02.491 --> 00:29:04.118
Can I ask you a personal question?

354
00:29:04.327 --> 00:29:06.037
Yeah, sure.

355
00:29:06.662 --> 00:29:08.623
How many times
did you take the test?

356
00:29:09.916 --> 00:29:13.210
What test?
You know, the test for detective.

357
00:29:13.377 --> 00:29:15.463
Oh! Yeah, that one!

358
00:29:15.755 --> 00:29:17.006
One time.
Really?

359
00:29:17.173 --> 00:29:19.008
Yeah. Aced it.
Really?

360
00:29:19.842 --> 00:29:21.344
Took it out.
Wow.

361
00:29:21.552 --> 00:29:23.804
Took me five tries.

362
00:29:24.305 --> 00:29:28.309
I did really well on the written part, you know,
but my performance reviews weren't so hot.

363
00:29:28.517 --> 00:29:32.188
Hey, look.
How many times did it take you to get your driver's licence, man?

364
00:29:32.355 --> 00:29:35.149
Please!
Wake me up when we get there.

365
00:29:35.358 --> 00:29:37.109
Yes, sir. I'm sorry.

366
00:29:37.318 --> 00:29:39.195
Goodness, man!

367
00:29:40.321 --> 00:29:42.657
It's a nice suit, sir.
It's really cool.

368
00:29:42.865 --> 00:29:44.533
Well, I appreciate it.

369
00:29:44.700 --> 00:29:46.702
Yeah, you know? Appreciate it.

370
00:29:46.994 --> 00:29:49.622
Got any music?
Oh, yeah. Sure.

371
00:29:50.414 --> 00:29:51.457
I like to jam.

372
00:29:53.209 --> 00:29:55.378
Just so long as
we can hear the dispatcher.

373
00:29:56.212 --> 00:29:57.630
That's good.

374
00:29:58.381 --> 00:30:01.759
