376
00:30:17.900 --> 00:30:19.402
Three dozen
gorgeous rims.

377
00:30:19.652 --> 00:30:20.820
They didn't take
anything else?

378
00:30:20.987 --> 00:30:25.533
No, they went for my good stuff.
Chrome with gold trim. Five grand worth.

379
00:30:26.534 --> 00:30:27.660
What about the alarm?

380
00:30:27.868 --> 00:30:29.745
What about it?
It went off.

381
00:30:29.912 --> 00:30:32.081
