404
00:31:22.923 --> 00:31:23.924
Long time.

405
00:31:24.091 --> 00:31:25.760
It would take a long time.
A very long time.

406
00:31:25.968 --> 00:31:29.430
Yeah, but they probably had about three
or four guys working the damn thing...

407
00:31:29.638 --> 00:31:31.974
Zip! Zip the shit up! Frank, hush.

408
00:31:32.308 --> 00:31:34.477
Okay? Because
you know better. Come on.

409
00:31:34.727 --> 00:31:38.606
Don't lie to me. I'm the man.
I'm the man, Frank.

410
00:31:38.814 --> 00:31:40.649
You're the man.
Frank,

411
00:31:40.816 --> 00:31:45.321
your 5000, sorry to tell you,
is worth less than 2 on the street.

