00:31:53.996 --> 00:31:55.498
Credit card,

415
00:31:56.207 --> 00:31:58.334
driver's licence.

416
00:31:59.251 --> 00:32:00.836
Unless, of course...

417
00:32:01.837 --> 00:32:03.339
you got your own truck.

418
00:32:05.424 --> 00:32:07.468
