00:33:02.565 --> 00:33:04.150
Thoroughly understand you.
That's right.

436
00:33:04.316 --> 00:33:07.820
Every time you look at your ass
there's gonna be a print there.

437
00:33:08.028 --> 00:33:09.822
It's gonna remind you of me
and my partner.

