439
00:33:12.658 --> 00:33:14.076
Don't wanna see those ridges.
All right. Hey, listen.

440
00:33:14.368 --> 00:33:17.621
Stop eating cold cuts, because it's seeping,
it's coming through your pores.

441
00:33:17.788 --> 00:33:20.166
All right?
Okay. Will do.

442
00:33:20.416 --> 00:33:23.002
I'll put one ridge
on your ass.

443
00:33:23.502 --> 00:33:26.922
Let's roll. That's cool.
Let's get out of here.

444
00:33:28.257 --> 00:33:31.385
Uh, yeah.
Detective, I know I'm a little bit new at this,

