I gotta get back. I got a headache.

486
00:35:58.824 --> 00:36:00.868
We're on duty, you know?
We'll get back when we get back.

487
00:36:01.076 --> 00:36:05.080
But I need an aspirin.
A big one, like a hockey puck.

488
00:36:05.247 --> 00:36:06.749
Gentlemen. Excuse me.

489
00:36:06.999 --> 00:36:09.001
Could you come here
for a second?

490
00:36:09.168 --> 00:36:11.712
